main event: An unidentified object, possibly a missile, was observed traveling from Pepperell AFB towards Thule, Greenland on 9 September 1953.
interesting points: The object was visually observed for 7-8 minutes,The object traveled at a high rate of speed,The sighting occurred at night time at 2100 hours,The course of the object was west,There were no photographs or physical evidence found.
